name: SPIRIT IN THE LAUNDROMAT
description:
Some say if you're the only one in the Washateria, he appears faintly in the edge of your vision. Don't worry, he's friendly, simply existing to keep those without in-unit laundry from getting too lonely while they wait.

IMAGINED OIL ON CANVAS: VQGAN PROCESSING OF ORIGINAL PAINTING BY CHRIS MCCULLY (SPINK DINKY) 2021
